# Changes in 0.15.5 (date: 2017/06/14)
  [기능추가]
  1. 사진첨부기능 추가

  [버그수정]
  1. 첨부사진 삭제시 순서가 바뀌는 오류수정
  2. RecognizerIntent 없는경우 발생하는 App Crash 오류수정

  [기타]
  1. update realm schema version(4)

  [New Feature]
  1. Added photo attachment feature to diary

  [Fixed Bug]
  1. Fixed an error that changed the order when deleting attached pictures
  2. Fixed App Crash error when there is no RecognizerIntent

  [Etc]
  1. update realm schema version(4)

